name: Tiffany
description: [Demon | Assassin] "Demonic Stealth" Activate: In your MP1, For 2 turn, Tiffany cannot be targeted during the Battle Phase. If Tiffany attacks, her stealth breaks dealing giving her a 50% chance to deal +15% Crit DMG . Cooldown: 3 turns.
